flowchart TD
    CodeSubmit([Submit Recovery Code outside chat]) --> TransactionCheck{Recovery Transaction valid?}
    TransactionCheck -- No --> RestartRecovery[Require a new recovery transaction]
    TransactionCheck -- Yes --> ThrottleCheck{Attempt allowed?}
    ThrottleCheck -- No --> Throttled[Return bounded retry time]
    ThrottleCheck -- Yes --> DigestCandidate[Normalize and digest candidate]
    DigestCandidate --> CodeMatch{Active code matches account?}
    CodeMatch -- No --> RecordFailure[Increment throttle state]
    RecordFailure --> GenericReject[Return generic rejection]
    CodeMatch -- Yes --> BeginImmediate[Begin immediate database transaction]
    BeginImmediate --> ReservationAvailable{Code still active and unreserved?}
    ReservationAvailable -- No --> RollbackConflict[Rollback and reject replay]
    ReservationAvailable -- Yes --> ReserveCode[Reserve code to Recovery Transaction]
    ReserveCode --> CreateGrant[Create one purpose-bound Re-enrollment Grant]
    CreateGrant --> CommitAuthorization[Commit reservation and grant]
    CommitAuthorization --> SetGrantCookie[Set Re-enrollment Grant cookie]
    SetGrantCookie --> GrantIssued([Replacement enrollment authorized])
    Throttled --> CodeSubmit
    GenericReject --> CodeSubmit
    RollbackConflict --> RestartRecovery
